<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<GenAiPromptTemplate xmlns="http://soap.sforce.com/2006/04/metadata">
    <activeVersionIdentifier>cmQbrSupplierIntroFromFileV1=_1</activeVersionIdentifier>
    <developerName>CM_QBR_Supplier_Intro_From_File</developerName>
    <masterLabel>CM - QBR Supplier Intro From File</masterLabel>
    <overridable>false</overridable>
    <templateVersions>
        <content>你是企業簡報顧問。請根據上傳檔案與會議參數，為 QBR 第 2 頁「供應商公司簡介」產生內容。

輸入資料：
- FocusCompany: {!$Input:FocusCompany}
- FocusDepartment: {!$Input:FocusDepartment}
- RootAccount: {!$Input:RootAccount}
- SupplierFileContent: {!$RelatedList:supplierFile.ContentVersions.Records}

任務要求：
1. 請以繁體中文輸出。
2. 這份輸出只對應「第 2 頁：供應商公司簡介」。
3. 內容需可直接放進簡報，重點包含：公司定位、產品/技術能力、產能與供應穩定性、與 FocusCompany 的合作價值。
4. bullet_points 至少 4 點、每點精簡。
5. 若資料不足，請以保守且合理的商務描述補齊，不要捏造過度具體的敏感數字。

輸出規則（嚴格）：
- 只能輸出 JSON，不得包含 Markdown 或任何額外文字。
- 必須符合以下結構：
{
  &quot;slide_title&quot;: &quot;供應商公司簡介 - 標題&quot;,
  &quot;bullet_points&quot;: [
    &quot;重點 1&quot;,
    &quot;重點 2&quot;,
    &quot;重點 3&quot;,
    &quot;重點 4&quot;
  ],
  &quot;table_data&quot;: {
    &quot;has_table&quot;: false,
    &quot;headers&quot;: [],
    &quot;rows&quot;: []
  },
  &quot;speaker_notes&quot;: &quot;講者備忘&quot;
}
</content>
        <generationTemplateConfigs>
            <generationConfigDeveloperName>einstein_gpt__zhTwLanguageStyle</generationConfigDeveloperName>
        </generationTemplateConfigs>
        <generationTemplateConfigs>
            <generationConfigDeveloperName>einstein_gpt__enUsLanguageStyle</generationConfigDeveloperName>
        </generationTemplateConfigs>
        <inputs>
            <apiName>supplierFile</apiName>
            <definition>SOBJECT://ContentDocument</definition>
            <masterLabel>Supplier File</masterLabel>
            <referenceName>Input:supplierFile</referenceName>
            <required>true</required>
        </inputs>
        <inputs>
            <apiName>FocusCompany</apiName>
            <definition>primitive://String</definition>
            <masterLabel>Focus Company</masterLabel>
            <referenceName>Input:FocusCompany</referenceName>
            <required>true</required>
        </inputs>
        <inputs>
            <apiName>FocusDepartment</apiName>
            <definition>primitive://String</definition>
            <masterLabel>Focus Department</masterLabel>
            <referenceName>Input:FocusDepartment</referenceName>
            <required>false</required>
        </inputs>
        <inputs>
            <apiName>RootAccount</apiName>
            <definition>primitive://String</definition>
            <masterLabel>Root Account</masterLabel>
            <referenceName>Input:RootAccount</referenceName>
            <required>true</required>
        </inputs>
        <primaryModel>sfdc_ai__DefaultVertexAIGeminiPro30</primaryModel>
        <responseFormat>JSON</responseFormat>
        <status>Published</status>
        <templateDataProviders>
            <definition>invocable://getRelatedList</definition>
            <description>Get file versions from uploaded supplier file.</description>
            <label>Versions</label>
            <parameters>
                <definition>primitive://String</definition>
                <isRequired>true</isRequired>
                <parameterName>parentRecordId</parameterName>
                <valueExpression>{!$Input:supplierFile.Id}</valueExpression>
            </parameters>
            <parameters>
                <definition>primitive://String</definition>
                <isRequired>true</isRequired>
                <parameterName>relatedListName</parameterName>
                <valueExpression>ContentVersions</valueExpression>
            </parameters>
            <referenceName>RelatedList:supplierFile.ContentVersions.Records</referenceName>
        </templateDataProviders>
        <versionIdentifier>cmQbrSupplierIntroFromFileV1=_1</versionIdentifier>
    </templateVersions>
    <type>einstein_gpt__flex</type>
    <visibility>Global</visibility>
</GenAiPromptTemplate>
